Believe and trust that as it is easy for you to breathe the air and
live by it. or to eat and drink, so it is easy and even still easier
for your faith to receive all spiritual gifts from the Lord. Prayer
is the breathing of the soulï¼š prayer is our spiritual food and
drink.
